'''Ed Hannigan''' (born [[August 6]], [[1950s#1951|1951]]) is a comic book illustrator who worked on a few issues in the [[Star Wars (1977)|''Marvel Star Wars'']] comic series. Hannigan began in the comic industry in the 1970s pencilling several titles at [[Marvel Comics|Marvel]] and [[Wikipedia:DC Comics|DC Comics]] including [[Wikipedia:Defenders (comics)|''Defenders'']] and [[Wikipedia:Green Arrow|''Green Arrow'']]. However, most of his work was in comic cover design and illustration through the decades.

